channel.title: Comments on: Daft.ie partners with eBay

item.title: By: Niall Larkin
item.dc:creator: Niall Larkin
item.description: Very interesting. Always fascinated by deals like this. I would love to hear from someone willing to put forward an educated guess (or even a random wild guess) about how that partnership might have been structured. Where would they even start?
